{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/ayang","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"ayang"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Wayfinding System Design for Ayang Bridge","author":"Minkyoung Lee, Prof. Baek Myungjin, A&C company","date":"November 15th, 2013","hero_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.4150943396226414,"src":"/static/ee4bb4567f07a7d7bb519bfc77a0d3cd/398d8/ayang-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ee4bb4567f07a7d7bb519bfc77a0d3cd/8def4/ayang-1.jpg 375w,\n/static/ee4bb4567f07a7d7bb519bfc77a0d3cd/35c3d/ayang-1.jpg 750w,\n/static/ee4bb4567f07a7d7bb519bfc77a0d3cd/398d8/ayang-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/ee4bb4567f07a7d7bb519bfc77a0d3cd/055c0/ayang-1.jpg 2000w","sizes":"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"}}}},"html":"<p>The bridge is an unused train track in the Daegu province in South Korea. Instead of eliminating this architecture, we worked on a project to create a new cultural space by creating a museum and a shelter here.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.800000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang ci 1\"\n        title=\"ayang ci 1\"\n        src=\"/static/69e715ce054684c27479c893d79fa3f7/a2510/ayang-ci-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/69e715ce054684c27479c893d79fa3f7/0479a/ayang-ci-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/69e715ce054684c27479c893d79fa3f7/41099/ayang-ci-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/69e715ce054684c27479c893d79fa3f7/a2510/ayang-ci-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/69e715ce054684c27479c893d79fa3f7/6b04e/ayang-ci-1.jpg 1150w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.800000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang ci 2\"\n        title=\"ayang ci 2\"\n        src=\"/static/064059f8ed68819a162eae5a4ba692c6/a2510/ayang-ci-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/064059f8ed68819a162eae5a4ba692c6/0479a/ayang-ci-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/064059f8ed68819a162eae5a4ba692c6/41099/ayang-ci-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/064059f8ed68819a162eae5a4ba692c6/a2510/ayang-ci-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/064059f8ed68819a162eae5a4ba692c6/6b04e/ayang-ci-2.jpg 1150w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We developed the logo of Ayang brdige based on its external shape of the side and the front. Long shape of the museum is divided into three different areas. We naturally made the cut triangle shape of the building cut into small logos of the spaces, and the shape viewed from the side of the museum became the logo representing the Ayang Bridge.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang plan 1\"\n        title=\"ayang plan 1\"\n        src=\"/static/81d5583a49812c05a526d15953c3ce1a/a2510/ayang-plan-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/81d5583a49812c05a526d15953c3ce1a/0479a/ayang-plan-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/81d5583a49812c05a526d15953c3ce1a/41099/ayang-plan-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/81d5583a49812c05a526d15953c3ce1a/a2510/ayang-plan-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/81d5583a49812c05a526d15953c3ce1a/e5166/ayang-plan-1.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang plan 2\"\n        title=\"ayang plan 2\"\n        src=\"/static/de746865c6e43eadec274808cfce5b08/a2510/ayang-plan-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/de746865c6e43eadec274808cfce5b08/0479a/ayang-plan-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/de746865c6e43eadec274808cfce5b08/41099/ayang-plan-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/de746865c6e43eadec274808cfce5b08/a2510/ayang-plan-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/de746865c6e43eadec274808cfce5b08/e5166/ayang-plan-2.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang plan 3\"\n        title=\"ayang plan 3\"\n        src=\"/static/491325b28daed66860f141f5b4ea639a/a2510/ayang-plan-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/491325b28daed66860f141f5b4ea639a/0479a/ayang-plan-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/491325b28daed66860f141f5b4ea639a/41099/ayang-plan-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/491325b28daed66860f141f5b4ea639a/a2510/ayang-plan-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/491325b28daed66860f141f5b4ea639a/e5166/ayang-plan-3.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We made a user flow of the museum. The museum is formed in the shape of a long tunnel along the railroad bridge. Since there are no other entrances in the middle, all the space users can enter and leave will be the front entrances and exit of the back. But we had to consider people not only entering or leaving the museum but also walking inside. Therefore, we drew user scenarios considering people outside and inside the structure. We wanted to make clear of outer passageways so that people wouldn't twist the lines in the narrow streets.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang plan 4\"\n        title=\"ayang plan 4\"\n        src=\"/static/1d22e143213cbb1d2d1debf9087fe248/a2510/ayang-plan-4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d22e143213cbb1d2d1debf9087fe248/0479a/ayang-plan-4.jpg 250w,\n/static/1d22e143213cbb1d2d1debf9087fe248/41099/ayang-plan-4.jpg 500w,\n/static/1d22e143213cbb1d2d1debf9087fe248/a2510/ayang-plan-4.jpg 1000w,\n/static/1d22e143213cbb1d2d1debf9087fe248/c58a3/ayang-plan-4.jpg 1500w,\n/static/1d22e143213cbb1d2d1debf9087fe248/8307e/ayang-plan-4.jpg 1667w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We made four types of signages. And place them regarding the user scenarios. Orderly we indicated the signages in the building's development figure. Orderly 1)Comprehensive guide signs, 2)caution guide signs, 3)facility guide signs, and 4)other guide signs.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang sign 1\"\n        title=\"ayang sign 1\"\n        src=\"/static/b00bfc4c10ab12e7c384d587b9245b55/a2510/ayang-sign-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b00bfc4c10ab12e7c384d587b9245b55/0479a/ayang-sign-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/b00bfc4c10ab12e7c384d587b9245b55/41099/ayang-sign-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/b00bfc4c10ab12e7c384d587b9245b55/a2510/ayang-sign-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/b00bfc4c10ab12e7c384d587b9245b55/c58a3/ayang-sign-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/b00bfc4c10ab12e7c384d587b9245b55/d9c39/ayang-sign-1.jpg 1800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>The direction of the diagonal line commonly applied to the two types of the bridge upper building structure and the above-ground part was reflected on the design of signages.<br>\nFor the material and finishing treatment, rust prevention treatment and fluorine coating were applied to the steel panel.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 154.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang sign 2\"\n        title=\"ayang sign 2\"\n        src=\"/static/498e9c29f14792f53a2e1a48f5b90d61/a2510/ayang-sign-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/498e9c29f14792f53a2e1a48f5b90d61/0479a/ayang-sign-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/498e9c29f14792f53a2e1a48f5b90d61/41099/ayang-sign-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/498e9c29f14792f53a2e1a48f5b90d61/a2510/ayang-sign-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/498e9c29f14792f53a2e1a48f5b90d61/c58a3/ayang-sign-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/498e9c29f14792f53a2e1a48f5b90d61/3acf0/ayang-sign-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/498e9c29f14792f53a2e1a48f5b90d61/808d7/ayang-sign-2.jpg 4535w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Comprehensive signage and direction signage is placed on all exits. Distances to main places from the signage are marked.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 127.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang sign 5\"\n        title=\"ayang sign 5\"\n        src=\"/static/6c91731b567945cc3ba9035646eec89b/a2510/ayang-sign-5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6c91731b567945cc3ba9035646eec89b/0479a/ayang-sign-5.jpg 250w,\n/static/6c91731b567945cc3ba9035646eec89b/41099/ayang-sign-5.jpg 500w,\n/static/6c91731b567945cc3ba9035646eec89b/a2510/ayang-sign-5.jpg 1000w,\n/static/6c91731b567945cc3ba9035646eec89b/c58a3/ayang-sign-5.jpg 1500w,\n/static/6c91731b567945cc3ba9035646eec89b/3acf0/ayang-sign-5.jpg 2000w,\n/static/6c91731b567945cc3ba9035646eec89b/b541c/ayang-sign-5.jpg 3400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Main design signage is designed differently from the general signages. Considering user experiences and the branding of Ayang bridge, we applied mapes and logo to the signage and tilted it. We intended to make users want to enter the building.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang view 1\"\n        title=\"ayang view 1\"\n        src=\"/static/59d96ae72bc3f441e9ef7b35c91750db/a2510/ayang-view-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/59d96ae72bc3f441e9ef7b35c91750db/0479a/ayang-view-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/59d96ae72bc3f441e9ef7b35c91750db/41099/ayang-view-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/59d96ae72bc3f441e9ef7b35c91750db/a2510/ayang-view-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/59d96ae72bc3f441e9ef7b35c91750db/c58a3/ayang-view-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/59d96ae72bc3f441e9ef7b35c91750db/3acf0/ayang-view-1.jpg 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ayang view 2\"\n        title=\"ayang view 2\"\n        src=\"/static/e61d0ab3f18a79014c226794c2fbed0e/a2510/ayang-view-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e61d0ab3f18a79014c226794c2fbed0e/0479a/ayang-view-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/e61d0ab3f18a79014c226794c2fbed0e/41099/ayang-view-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/e61d0ab3f18a79014c226794c2fbed0e/a2510/ayang-view-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/e61d0ab3f18a79014c226794c2fbed0e/c58a3/ayang-view-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/e61d0ab3f18a79014c226794c2fbed0e/3acf0/ayang-view-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/e61d0ab3f18a79014c226794c2fbed0e/9c9b2/ayang-view-2.jpg 2268w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Client | Gyeongsangbuk-do province Dae-gu\nResponsibilities | logo production, sign system design and production</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"ayang"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2708967481","3255264069"]}